<!doctype html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>MesosTerm</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/static/ico/favicon.ico">
</head>

<body>
  <p>This endpoint allows super admins to delegate rights to login into a specific container.</p>
  <p>In order to delegate rights to log into task ID <b>XXXX</b> to <b>john</b> during <b>1h</b>, you can type the
    following command:</p>
  <p style="border: 1px solid black; background-color: #ececec; padding: 20px; vertical-align: middle;">
    curl -u "<%= user %>" -XPOST -d '{"task_id": "XXXX", "delegate_to": "john", "duration": "1h"}' -H "Content-Type:
    application/json" <%= url %>/api/delegate
  </p>
</body>

</html>
